    dc:title "A Review of the Genus Curculio from China with Descriptions of Fourteen New Species. Part IV. The Curculio sikkimensis (Heller) Group (Coleoptera: Curculionidae: Curculioninae: Curculionini)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10103727>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10103731>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10103729>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10103733>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10103737>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10103741>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10103739> ;
