<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10103727>
    dc:description "Figs. 1–2. Curculio hsifanus (Heller) Male, habitus dorsal and lateral views. Figs. 3–4. Curculio c-album Fabricius Male, habitus dorsal and lateral views. Figs. 5–6. Curculio pylzovi (Smirnov) Male, habitus dorsal and lateral views. Fig. 6. Arrow indicates small tooth. Various scales." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10103727/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10103731>
    dc:description "Figs. 13–14. Curculio zangi n. sp. Female, habitus dorsal and lateral views, holotype. Figs. 15–16. Curculio nigra n. sp. Female, habitus dorsal and lateral views, holotype. Figs. 17–18. Curculio dijoui n. sp. Female, habitus dorsal and lateral views, holotype. Various scales." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10103731/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10103729>
    dc:description "Figs. 7–8. Curculio hippophes Zhang Female, habitus dorsal and lateral views. Figs. 9–10. Curculio sikkimensis (Heller) Male, habitus dorsal and lateral views. Figs. 11–12. Curculio penteri n. sp. Male, habitus dorsal and lateral views, holotype. Various scales." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10103729/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10103733>
    dc:description "Figs. 19–20. Curculio mullai n. sp. Female, habitus dorsal and lateral views, holotype. Figs. 21–22. Curculio megadens n. sp. Male, habitus dorsal and lateral views, holotype. Figs. 23–24. Curculio careoparvus n. sp. Male, habitus dorsal and lateral views, holotype. Fig. 24. Arrow indicates medium tooth. Various scales." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10103733/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10103737>
    dc:description "Figs. 25–26. Curculio brevidens n. sp. Female, habitus dorsal and lateral views, holotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10103737/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10103741>
    dc:description "Figs. 37–38. Curculio lyali. n. sp. Male, habitus dorsal and lateral views, holotype. Various scales." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10103741/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10103739>
    dc:description "Figs. 31–32. Curculio pascoei n. sp. Male, habitus dorsal and lateral views, holotype. Figs. 33–34. Curculio hobbsi n. sp. Male, habitus dorsal and lateral views, holotype. Figs. 35–36. Curculio songi n. sp. Male, habitus dorsal and lateral views, holotype. Various scales." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10103739/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

